deadZoneLow.title: Low Dead Zone
deadZoneLow.description: Radial thickness of inner dead zone of pad's joysticks. This dead zone ensures that all pads report a value of 0 for each joystick axis when untouched.

deadZoneHigh.title: High Dead Zone
deadZoneHigh.description: Radial thickness of outer dead zone of pad's joysticks. This dead zone ensures that all pads can reach the -1 and 1 limits of each joystick axis.

turnSpeed.title: Turn Speed
turnSpeed.description: Maximum turn speed in degrees per second

deadZone.title: Dead Zone
deadZone.description: Radial thickness of inner dead zone of the virtual joysticks. This dead zone ensures the virtual joysticks report a value of 0 even if a touch deviates a small amount from the initial touch.

turnSpeed.title: Turn Speed
turnSpeed.description: Maximum turn speed in degrees per second

radius.title: Radius
radius.description: The radius of the virtual joystick in CSS pixels.

_doubleTapInterval.title: Double Tap Interval
_doubleTapInterval.description: The time in milliseconds between two taps of the right virtual joystick for a double tap to register. A double tap will trigger a cc:jump.

targetPosition.title: Target Position
targetPosition.description: The position to teleport the player to

targetRotation.title: Target Rotation
targetRotation.description: Euler angles (X, Y, Z in degrees) for rotation after teleport

zoomSpeed.description: Player's camera zoom speed, in degrees

minFov.description: Maximum amount of zoom for player's camera

footstepsPeriod.description: Footsteps sound period: the larger the value, the less frequent are footstep sounds

layer.title: Layer
layer.description: Has to be between a value of 3 and 14. 3 being the highest priority

keepUpdating.title: Keep Updating
keepUpdating.description: Update the shape data every frame (only toggle if the entity moves as can be expensive)

childOfActualEntity.title: Child Of Actual Entity
childOfActualEntity.description: Tick if the shape is a child of the actual entity object

soundSlotName.title: Sound Slot Name
soundSlotName.description: Name of slot to play on Hifi

compatibleTag.title: Compatible Tag
compatibleTag.description: Tag that this object can interact with

presetEntity.title: Preset Entity
presetEntity.description: Entity to be attached to this on start

targetPosition.title: Target Position
targetPosition.description: The position to TeleportVRroom the player to

targetRotation.title: Target Rotation
targetRotation.description: Euler angles (X, Y, Z in degrees) for rotation after TeleportVRroom

playerEntity.title: Player Entity
playerEntity.description: Direct reference to the player entity (overrides player tag if set)

playerTag.description: Fallback: Tag for player entity if no entity is specified
